    Dependent tree map lemmas #

    This file contains lemmas about Std.Data.DTreeMap.Raw.Basic. Most of the lemmas require TransCmp cmp for the comparison function cmp and a proof that the involved maps are well-formed. These proofs can be obtained from Std.Data.DTreeMap.Raw.WF.
